{"type":null,"faqId":32989,"title":"新建联系人后出现手机白屏或卡顿怎么办","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">新增的联系人默认是保存到“手机”帐户中，当手机帐户异常时会出现该问题。可在联系人帐户中添加“华为云服务”帐户来解决此问题。添加方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、进入设置-帐户（华为云服务），注册华为云服务的账号。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、进入联系人-点击右下角的菜单-帐户-添加华为云服务。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7691","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748467000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":18,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"新建联系人,白屏,卡顿","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}